1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:02,810
While Oh Jang Mi is busy
pretending to be Ma Seo Rin,

2
00:00:03,110 --> 00:00:05,680
I'm going to act like a real mother
to Ma Seo Rin.

3
00:00:06,280 --> 00:00:09,480
And when I make my move,
I'll finish it all at once.

4
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:12,180
You know what I mean, don't you?

5
00:00:13,020 --> 00:00:14,020
Understood.

6
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,550
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

7
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:22,560
I've poured my entire life
into getting this far.

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:25,400
There's no way I'm letting them
take it from me.

9
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,170
Oh Jang Mi.

10
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:28,970
You'd better be ready.

11
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:33,170
Because I am going to stomp you
into the ground.

12
00:00:35,370 --> 00:00:38,280
So, did you get through the eye exam okay?

13
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:40,810
Yes. Thanks to you,

14
00:00:40,950 --> 00:00:42,680
I don't think
Chae Hwa Young is suspicious any longer.

15
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,880
I even managed to memorize
the eye chart in a flash.

16
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:48,290
You'd be surprised at what you can do
when you're backed into a corner.

17
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:50,660
I guess so.

18
00:00:51,120 --> 00:00:52,590
I'm still worried, though.

19
00:00:53,060 --> 00:00:55,430
I know because I've dealt with
CEO Chae for a long time.

20
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:59,360
The fact that she made you get an eye exam
proves she's suspicious of you.

21
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,330
Yes, I'm staying on my toes.

22
00:01:03,370 --> 00:01:06,540
I need to find the dashcam footage
of my dad's accident soon.

23
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:09,210
I tore through Chae Hwa Young's room,
but I couldn't find anything.

24
00:01:09,310 --> 00:01:12,710
I know.
You can't keep fooling CEO Chae forever.

25
00:01:12,940 --> 00:01:14,280
This is so worrying.

26
00:01:14,350 --> 00:01:17,180
I guess I'll have to search
Chae Hwa Young's office next.

27
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:19,650
I have to find it one way or another
before she destroys it.

28
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,090
What?

29
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,350
What did you just ask me to do?

30
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,590
You want me to spy on Oh Tae Pyung?

31
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:27,460
Why do you seem so happy about it?

32
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,630
No.

33
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:30,800
What are you talking about?

34
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:33,260
Why would I be happy
spying on Oh Tae Pyung?

35
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:37,340
You've been boy-crazy since we were kids.

36
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:38,640
Hey, Chae Hwa Young!

37
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:41,640
When we were in school,
you only hung around me...

38
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:44,240
to get to the guys who liked me.

39
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:48,350
You think I don't know why
you're a stylist to get close to celebs?

40
00:01:48,410 --> 00:01:49,610
That's not true!

41
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:52,750
You think I have no professional pride?

42
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,890
I enjoyed my job. It was fulfilling.

43
00:01:56,050 --> 00:01:57,560
Right, whatever you say.

44
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,330
While you spy on Oh Tae Pyung,

45
00:02:00,330 --> 00:02:03,130
watch over his family by visiting
the side dish shop too.

46
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:07,400
Hwa Young,
I'm just really curious about something.

47
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:11,400
Oh Jang Mi is your daughter, isn't she?

48
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,910
But why did you leave her
with that family?

49
00:02:13,970 --> 00:02:15,370
Yeom San Wol, do you have a death wish?

50
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,780
If you keep running your stupid mouth,

51
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,710
I'll leak the photos of your affair.

52
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,450
Should I just leak them?

53
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:24,320
No, that's not what I meant!

54
00:02:24,420 --> 00:02:27,320
Say one more ridiculous thing like that,
and I swear I'll...

55
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,960
My lips are sealed!

56
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:34,960
I'm sorry. I was out of line.

57
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:37,060
If you keep your end of the bargain,

58
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:40,030
I might even set your daughter up...

59
00:02:40,030 --> 00:02:42,100
with the youngest son
of a conglomerate family.

60
00:02:42,300 --> 00:02:43,640
- Really?
- So from now on,

61
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,570
do exactly as I say.

62
00:02:46,070 --> 00:02:48,940
Trust only my words
and do exactly what I say.

63
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:52,680
If what you're saying is true,
how affluent is that family ranked?

64
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:01,120
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

65
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:05,260
Jun Ho, come and sit with me.
We need to talk.

66
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:09,460
You're just as bad as Director Ma
when it comes to interrupting my work.

67
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:13,570
Has Kang Baek Ho said anything to you
about Seo Rin?

68
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:15,770
Like what?

69
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:19,100
Are you asking if I told him
that I was marrying Seo Rin?

70
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:21,210
Yes, I did.

71
00:03:22,010 --> 00:03:24,410
So it seems Kang Baek Ho didn't mention
anything about Oh Jang Mi.

72
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,050
Why are you staring at me like that?

73
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:29,350
If that's all,
can you please leave me to work?

74
00:03:31,850 --> 00:03:33,550
Fine. Get back to work.

75
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,900
You're here too, ma'am?

76
00:03:44,330 --> 00:03:46,600
Team Leader Jin, see me
after you get that approved.

77
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,500
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

78
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:57,010
What? You want me to spy on Seo Rin?

79
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,140
That's right.

80
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:01,110
From now on,
I want you to stick to Seo Rin like glue,

81
00:04:01,710 --> 00:04:03,780
find out who she's meeting,
what she's doing,

82
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,220
and report every last detail to me.

83
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,690
Me?

84
00:04:08,490 --> 00:04:10,590
- I don't think I can...
- Are you saying no?

85
00:04:10,790 --> 00:04:12,320
No, it's not that, it's just...

86
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:16,290
How am I supposed to do that?
Director Ma is so sharp...

87
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,500
that I'll be caught in no time.

88
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,570
Then make sure you don't get caught.

89
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,530
If you can't do this,

90
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:25,340
I might get you and your mother
thrown out empty-handed.

91
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:26,900
It's up to you.

92
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:28,310
Ma'am, please...

93
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:31,910
What do you think the Chairman will say
when he sees photos of her affair?

94
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,750
Understood. I'll do as you say.

95
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:36,950
You should have just agreed
in the first place.

96
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,150
I'm heading out for the day.

97
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:41,550
Team Leader Jin, you're driving.

98
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,150
Pardon?

99
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:06,440
She spends most of her day in here,

100
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:09,450
so she might keep anything important
in here.

101
00:05:09,910 --> 00:05:11,650
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

102
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:18,820
In the shows I've watched,
they always have a hidden safe.

103
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:30,900
What?

104
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:33,340
Seo Rin's car is there,

105
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:35,810
but she's nowhere to be found
in the building?

106
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:39,380
- What about my office?
- We haven't checked...

107
00:05:39,510 --> 00:05:42,550
Go up and check my office.
I'm on my way there now.

108
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:54,730
Hong Ju.

109
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:11,080
What's this?
Why are they looking for Seo Rin?

110
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:12,540
Are they onto something?

111
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:19,750
- The person you're calling is...
- Why isn't she picking up?

112
00:06:22,850 --> 00:06:23,860
Hey, what's gotten into you?

113
00:06:23,990 --> 00:06:26,890
Mom, do you have any idea the humiliation
I just went through because of you?

114
00:06:27,490 --> 00:06:28,760
You mean from CEO Chae?

115
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:32,230
She told me to spy on Ma Seo Rin.

116
00:06:32,230 --> 00:06:33,230
She told you that, too?

117
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,170
That Chae Hwa Young.

118
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:37,600
Wasn't I enough?
Now she's going after my daughter?

119
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:41,140
- This is infuriating.
- Did she tell you to spy on Seo Rin, too?

120
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:45,240
My orders were to keep an eye on
Oh Jang Mi's side dish shop.

121
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:47,710
Did she use the photos of your affair
to blackmail you, too?

122
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:49,810
Yes.

123
00:06:49,810 --> 00:06:52,020
Mom, you're going to be the death of me.

124
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:55,690
What is this?
She has us completely under her thumb.

125
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,620
If only the DNA test
for Hwa Young and Seo Rin...

126
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:00,190
had shown they weren't a match,

127
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:03,060
we could have told the Chairman,
and it would've been game over for her.

128
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:07,430
I guess no matter what I do,

129
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:10,500
I'm destined to be Hwa Young's gofer.

130
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:14,710
But Mom, CEO Chae must have
something she's hiding.

131
00:07:15,170 --> 00:07:19,240
Why else would she make us watch
Ma Seo Rin and Oh Jang Mi's shop?

132
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,750
- What?
- If they're just look-alikes, not twins,

133
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:25,720
then CEO Chae wouldn't be
this concerned about it.

134
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:28,390
You know, that's true.

135
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,750
In that case,

136
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,420
we need to figure out why
CEO Chae gave birth to twins...

137
00:07:32,690 --> 00:07:34,690
and kept one and abandoned the other.

138
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:36,830
That's the mystery we have to solve.

139
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,800
- Thank you.
- Have a good day!

140
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:45,070
Mom has a fever.
I think she's coming down with a cold.

141
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:47,540
Really? Did you give her some medicine?

142
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,840
Of course I did.

143
00:07:56,410 --> 00:08:00,380
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

144
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:12,530
I finally found it!

145
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:14,230
Chae Hwa Young's safe.

146
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,150
- Baek Ho.
- What are you doing here at this hour?

147
00:08:35,950 --> 00:08:37,890
I was on my way here
after getting a call from Geum Soon.

148
00:08:38,290 --> 00:08:41,190
She said she couldn't reach you,
so I came to check. And here you are.

149
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:43,590
But what are you doing in here?
It's dangerous.

150
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,800
Take a look at this.

151
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,930
So you were looking for the memory card
from the parking lot dashcam.

152
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:52,600
Yes, I thought it might be in here.

153
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:56,240
But I don't think this safe
will be easy to open.

154
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:58,040
Let me ask AI.

155
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:06,280
Hold on a second.

156
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:07,390
This safe...

157
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,550
locks you out for three minutes
every time you enter the wrong code.

158
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:13,090
It locks you out for three minutes?
Every single time?

159
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,330
Yes, and we only get three tries.

160
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:17,090
After that, an alarm will go off.

161
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,070
Finding the passcode is our top priority.

162
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:22,570
If we make one wrong move,

163
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:24,700
the guards will come running,
and this will become a huge problem.

164
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:27,270
Let's open it while Chae Hwa Young is out.
What should we do?

165
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,240
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

166
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,780
I'll try Chae Hwa Young's birthday.

167
00:09:32,110 --> 00:09:33,410
My hands are shaking.

168
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:38,480
Six, eight, zero, four.

169
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:45,260
Was Hwa Young really just trying
to use me?

170
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:48,730
No, it can't be. That's not it.

171
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:50,230
It can't be.

172
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,760
Why are you drinking all alone,
looking so miserable?

173
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,740
Here, let me join you.

174
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,040
Goodness.

175
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:07,980
Alright.

176
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:12,050
It's been a while
since you wanted to have a drink with me.

177
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:16,190
So what's got you so upset?

178
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,160
Young Ja.

179
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:25,930
Am I a good husband and a good father?

180
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:30,200
- Am I?
- Why would you ask? Of course you are.

181
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:34,140
The kids absolutely adore you.
You won't find another family like ours.

182
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,240
And to you?

183
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:40,340
You're the best husband there is.

184
00:10:43,410 --> 00:10:46,850
I wouldn't trade my life with anyone.

185
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:52,760
You've never cheated on me
or gotten into any financial trouble.

186
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,660
And you're so good
at keeping your promises.

187
00:10:56,490 --> 00:11:00,430
You're a family man who only ever thinks
about the kids and me.

188
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,700
But, honey,

189
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:10,010
now that I'm taking a closer look,
where did all these wrinkles come from?

190
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:13,280
Goodness, you need to start
taking better care of your skin.

191
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:16,310
It's all about looks these days.

192
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,020
If you changed your hairstyle,

193
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,350
I think you'd look a lot younger.

194
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:28,290
- I'm home.
- Jun Ho. Welcome home.

195
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:34,430
Does Hwa Young plan on
never seeing me again?

196
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:37,330
Is it because she really wants
Jun Ho as her son-in-law...

197
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:38,870
and is avoiding me?

198
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:40,910
Zero, four.

199
00:11:45,610 --> 00:11:48,110
No. That's not it.

200
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,780
Hurry up and try something else.

201
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,280
I have to wait three minutes.

202
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,950
Then what about Ma Seo Rin's birthday?

203
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:57,050
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

204
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:58,590
Yes, Mrs. Yang.

205
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,830
Jang Mi is with me right now.

206
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:03,390
You two aren't in CEO Chae's office,
are you?

207
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:06,200
How did you know?
We're in her office right now.

208
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:09,470
Get out of there now.
I heard Manager Lee is on his way there.

209
00:12:09,530 --> 00:12:10,670
And CEO Chae is on her way too.

210
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:12,170
Manager Lee is coming here?

211
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:48,110
Nine, five, one, zero, zero, one.

212
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,980
Okay, thanks for the heads-up.

213
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:58,520
It's not Seo Rin's birthday either.

214
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:00,650
Manager Lee is on his way here.

215
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:03,790
Let's stop for today
and try again another time.

216
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:08,860
We might not get another chance.
Let me use our last attempt.

217
00:13:08,930 --> 00:13:11,430
What if we get caught?
It's too risky, Jang Mi.

218
00:13:11,430 --> 00:13:13,030
Just one more try, please.

219
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,400
Alright, fine.

220
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:20,340
Think about someone
Chae Hwa Young cares about most,

221
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:22,070
or an object...

222
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:24,910
Think of a number
that would mean the most to her.

223
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:26,740
Chae Hwa Young?

224
00:13:34,050 --> 00:13:35,320
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

225
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:38,090
A number that's meaningful
to Chae Hwa Young...

226
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:44,030
May 29, 1990.

227
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:46,660
Must be the baby's birthday.

228
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:49,070
It's Kang Jun Ho's birthday.

229
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:58,840
Nine, zero, zero, five, two,

230
00:13:59,340 --> 00:14:00,340
nine.

231
00:14:11,090 --> 00:14:13,920
I don't think Baek Ho even knows
his brother was adopted.

232
00:14:14,430 --> 00:14:16,530
If he finds out that
Jun Ho is Chae Hwa Young's son,

233
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,430
I wonder how shocked he'd be.

234
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,630
I can't tell Baek Ho.

235
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:24,840
Listen, Manager Lee is coming,
so let's grab the things and leave.

236
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,240
This is it. The dashcam's memory card.

237
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:31,310
Look.

238
00:14:31,940 --> 00:14:33,610
- Don't tell me this is...
- Gosh.

239
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:37,820
This looks exactly like my dad's phone...

240
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,690
It is.

241
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:43,620
This is my dad's cell phone.

242
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:45,420
Let's just grab everything and go.

243
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:47,020
Come on!

244
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:52,000
What? You want to invite Director Ma over?

245
00:14:52,630 --> 00:14:54,600
- Yes.
- Does this mean...

246
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:58,040
you've finally decided
to marry Director Ma?

247
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,110
Yes, that's the plan.

248
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:04,780
I thought you said you didn't want
to marry Director Ma.

249
00:15:05,010 --> 00:15:07,110
Why the sudden change of heart?

250
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:10,550
I see now...

251
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,150
you're more ambitious than I thought.

252
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:15,990
Come on. What man isn't ambitious?

253
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:20,060
And besides,
you might as well go for the best.

254
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:23,030
It's so much better
to marry a rich woman...

255
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:26,260
than a girl from a dirt-poor family.

256
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:28,170
Sure.

257
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:34,410
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

258
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,210
Jang Mi isn't in the office.

259
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,290
Dad.

260
00:15:48,650 --> 00:15:51,390
CEO Chae had your father's phone
all this time.

261
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,290
Then that means...

262
00:15:53,690 --> 00:15:56,590
this is proof that CEO Chae was there
when your father died.

263
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,060
Exactly.

264
00:15:58,830 --> 00:16:02,530
And it's also proof that Chae Hwa Young
killed my dad.

265
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
There's blood here...

266
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:13,710
- Jang Mi.
- My dad died because of me.

267
00:16:14,850 --> 00:16:16,080
What am I going to do?

268
00:16:17,650 --> 00:16:19,380
Don't blame yourself so much, Jang Mi.

269
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:22,920
It's not your fault.
Chae Hwa Young did this.

270
00:16:23,990 --> 00:16:26,690
The crucial evidence has to be on here.

271
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:35,800
Look at this.

272
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:38,640
It's all on the dashcam.

273
00:17:00,290 --> 00:17:01,530
With this definitive evidence...

274
00:17:02,290 --> 00:17:04,660
and the fact that Chae Hwa Young
had your father's phone,

275
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:07,030
she won't be able to get away with it now.

276
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:11,240
I'll never forgive
that devil, Chae Hwa Young.

277
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:14,040
This means my father...

278
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:16,340
might be cleared of the charges too.

279
00:17:17,140 --> 00:17:20,380
Let's take this to the police now.

280
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,480
Okay.

281
00:17:21,850 --> 00:17:24,650
I'll make sure Chae Hwa Young pays
for what she did.

282
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:27,220
I'll clear my mom and dad's names,

283
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:30,550
and I'll make sure Chae Hwa Young
never sees the light of day again.

284
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:36,790
Jang Mi...

285
00:17:38,230 --> 00:17:40,100
I miss Jang Mi.

286
00:17:41,530 --> 00:17:43,170
Why won't her fever break?

287
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:47,000
Suk Hee...

288
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:49,170
Suk Hee's not sick.

289
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:51,240
Suk Hee's okay.

290
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:56,010
All right, Mom. I'll call Jang Mi
and tell her to come see you,

291
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,850
so just get some rest, okay?

292
00:17:58,550 --> 00:17:59,780
Jang Mi's coming.

293
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,650
Jang Mi's coming to see Suk Hee.

294
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,230
What?

295
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:14,630
Chae Hwa Young had Dad's phone?

296
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:16,170
What are you talking about?

297
00:18:16,930 --> 00:18:21,000
Tae Sook, Jang Mi found definitive proof
that Chae Hwa Young is the killer.

298
00:18:23,170 --> 00:18:24,680
Thank goodness.

299
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:28,650
We can finally start to clear Dad's name.

300
00:18:28,810 --> 00:18:32,380
Right. So you're off to the police station
with Baek Ho now?

301
00:18:34,850 --> 00:18:37,290
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

302
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:48,800
How can this be? It's gone.

303
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:50,670
There's nothing here!

304
00:18:50,930 --> 00:18:53,370
What am I going to do? What do I do?

305
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:55,370
What do you mean, it's gone?

306
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,310
Don't tell me...

307
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,280
you mean the memory card from the dashcam?

308
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:02,910
Oh Bok Gil's phone is missing,
and so is the memory card. It's gone!

309
00:19:03,050 --> 00:19:05,920
It was Oh Jang Mi. She stole them!

310
00:19:06,050 --> 00:19:08,050
What? Oh Bok Gil's phone?

311
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:11,020
You've had Oh Bok Gil's phone
this whole time?

312
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:15,430
I told you I should've gotten rid of it.
Why didn't you listen to me?

313
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:16,890
Is this really the time
for "I told you so"?

314
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,760
I was afraid I'd leave a trail
if I got rid of it carelessly,

315
00:19:20,030 --> 00:19:22,630
so I was keeping it
to throw in a river or something.

316
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:29,410
But I kept putting it off, and now,
that little rat Oh Jang Mi...

317
00:19:30,340 --> 00:19:31,410
What are we going to do?

318
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,580
She must've gone to the police.

319
00:19:33,810 --> 00:19:35,050
I'm sure she went straight there.

320
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:36,450
We have to stop her right now.

321
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:38,550
If she did, then it's already too late.

322
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,650
Too late?

323
00:19:42,390 --> 00:19:43,520
No.

324
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:45,690
They've probably seen the footage by now.

325
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,460
We're past the point
of chasing her down to stop her.

326
00:19:48,990 --> 00:19:50,160
Then what do we do?

327
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:53,000
- Should we just wait to be arrested?
- No.

328
00:19:54,730 --> 00:19:56,470
We make her come to us.

329
00:19:57,770 --> 00:19:58,800
Come to us?

330
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:00,900
With the evidence in hand,

331
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:02,910
we make her bring it to us herself.

332
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:07,280
Right.

333
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:09,110
You're right, Manager Lee.

334
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:12,680
We go after Oh Jang Mi's Achilles' heel.

335
00:20:13,220 --> 00:20:16,090
Right. We'd be at a disadvantage
if we went after her.

336
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:20,560
So we need to get our hands
on her biggest weakness, right?

337
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:23,160
Yes. I'll get her right away.

338
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:25,600
Wait.

339
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:27,830
Hold on a second.

340
00:20:29,300 --> 00:20:31,370
It's a bad move for us
to get directly involved.

341
00:20:39,110 --> 00:20:40,110
Yes, ma'am.

342
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:41,650
I need you to do something for me.

343
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:43,550
What? Me?

344
00:20:43,850 --> 00:20:45,080
I want you and your mother...

345
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:47,880
to go to the side dish shop right now...

346
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:49,650
and bring that woman, Jung Suk Hee, to me.

347
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:52,390
What? Bring her to you?

348
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:54,520
I don't have time for this.
Are you going to make me repeat myself?

349
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:59,300
Go now and bring Jung Suk Hee to me
without her family knowing.

350
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:02,630
- What?
- There's no time. Hurry up.

351
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:10,040
- Our Seo Rin?
- How about our families become in-laws?

352
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:14,040
What? You want me to give my Seo Rin
to that grandson of yours?

353
00:21:14,580 --> 00:21:15,580
The nerve of you.

354
00:21:15,650 --> 00:21:19,080
Don't play so hard to get.
I still outrank you in the business world.

355
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:22,220
Don't be ridiculous. I'm hanging up.

356
00:21:22,390 --> 00:21:23,790
Was that Chairman Lee?

357
00:21:24,490 --> 00:21:26,320
He's still going on about
business rankings from ages ago.

358
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:29,290
To think I have to listen to that
from a bottom-feeder like him.

359
00:21:33,860 --> 00:21:37,130
Father, I need to borrow Mom for a minute.

360
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:39,440
Why? Are you two going somewhere?

361
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:40,740
To get some exercise.

362
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:45,380
I've been so busy I haven't worked out,
and I think I'm gaining weight.

363
00:21:46,110 --> 00:21:48,210
We're just going for a quick walk
on the trail out front.

364
00:21:49,150 --> 00:21:50,450
Okay, go ahead.

365
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:02,430
Once San Wol and Hong Ju get Suk Hee out,

366
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:05,160
you grab her and bring her
to the warehouse quickly.

367
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:08,070
So we can use her as leverage
to deal with Oh Jang Mi?

368
00:22:08,430 --> 00:22:09,430
Exactly.

369
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:13,100
Let's see if she can still report it
to the police...

370
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,340
with her mother on the line.

371
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:16,240
We need to hurry.

372
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:19,240
We have to stay one step ahead
of Oh Jang Mi.

373
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:20,540
Because if we don't,

374
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:23,510
it's over for us
when the police get that evidence.

375
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:47,600
Since Oh Jang Mi's brother and sister
are at the store,

376
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:49,940
her mom must be home alone.

377
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,840
Hong Ju.

378
00:22:55,610 --> 00:22:58,420
Hong Ju, why are we doing this
to Jung Suk Hee?

379
00:22:58,620 --> 00:23:01,150
- This is kidnapping.
- You think I don't know that?

380
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:04,050
It's because of your affair photos, Mom.

381
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:05,220
If they get out,

382
00:23:05,290 --> 00:23:07,690
I'll get fired.
And that's not even the half of it.

383
00:23:07,760 --> 00:23:10,830
The Chairman will throw us out
on the street without a second thought.

384
00:23:11,290 --> 00:23:13,030
And you're worried about
kidnapping right now?

385
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:14,830
I can't believe you.

386
00:23:16,100 --> 00:23:17,470
I'm sorry, sweetie.

387
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:19,870
But even so,

388
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:22,170
if he finds out we kidnapped Jung Suk Hee,

389
00:23:22,610 --> 00:23:25,540
- my Tae Pyung would never let it go.
- Mom!

390
00:23:25,910 --> 00:23:28,080
And you're worried about "your Tae Pyung?"

391
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,280
Are you serious?

392
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:32,820
Gosh, my ears!
Alright! You don't have to shout.

393
00:23:32,950 --> 00:23:34,420
Good grief.

394
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:48,400
Detective Kim,
I have Oh Bok Gil's cell phone,

395
00:23:48,470 --> 00:23:49,770
and I've found the crucial evidence.

396
00:23:50,070 --> 00:23:51,600
I'd like to request
a digital forensic analysis.

397
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:54,170
The case is closed, but all right.

398
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:56,910
- Bring it in first.
- Yes, sir.

399
00:23:58,310 --> 00:23:59,440
He said to bring it in right away.

400
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:01,140
Let's hurry, Baek Ho.

401
00:24:06,280 --> 00:24:07,480
It's Jang Mi.

402
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:09,190
Jang Mi's here.

403
00:24:10,150 --> 00:24:11,790
I've missed you so much, Jang Mi.

404
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:18,930
You're not Jang Mi.

405
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:25,270
You remember me, don't you, Suk Hee?

406
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:26,940
It's nice to see you.

407
00:24:27,370 --> 00:24:30,710
Strangers aren't supposed to be in here.

408
00:24:30,710 --> 00:24:32,380
Oh, goodness.

409
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,580
Looks like you have a cold.

410
00:24:33,610 --> 00:24:35,110
Oh, dear.

411
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:38,680
- You're sweating so much...
- You recognize this photo, right?

412
00:24:40,250 --> 00:24:41,250
That's Tok Hee.

413
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,720
And this one?

414
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,820
That's Jang Mi.

415
00:24:48,490 --> 00:24:50,760
I can't really tell them apart.

416
00:24:50,990 --> 00:24:54,900
I know, right? They look identical.
It's incredible she can tell them apart.

417
00:24:55,530 --> 00:24:59,340
Oh Jang Mi is desperate to see her mother.

418
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:00,840
Don't you want to see her?

419
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:04,440
Jang Mi said she was coming to see me.

420
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,880
Jang Mi said she would come.

421
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:12,880
Do you hear that?
Sounds like it's coming from the annex.

422
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:14,420
Hold on.

423
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:36,740
(Yeongseo Police Department)

424
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:51,250
Nervous?

425
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:53,220
Yes.

426
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:56,330
To think this is finally coming to an end
is making me nervous.

427
00:25:56,730 --> 00:25:57,760
I'm nervous too.

428
00:25:59,130 --> 00:26:01,670
Your father will be completely
cleared of all charges.

429
00:26:01,670 --> 00:26:03,030
You must be thrilled, Baek Ho.

430
00:26:03,230 --> 00:26:06,740
Well, yes, there's that,
but once this is all taken care of,

431
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:10,070
all that's left is for us to go public
and get married.

432
00:26:11,340 --> 00:26:13,940
I don't know about all that.

433
00:26:15,410 --> 00:26:19,220
But about that passcode, 0529?
How did you know...?

434
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,150
Was it someone's birthday?

435
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:25,260
What was most precious to Chae Hwa Young?
I'm guessing it wasn't you.

436
00:26:26,390 --> 00:26:27,990
No, it's just...

437
00:26:28,890 --> 00:26:30,790
the day she became CEO.

438
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:33,800
I was just trying to think of a date
that would be meaningful to her.

439
00:26:34,260 --> 00:26:35,270
I see.

440
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:38,870
I thought it was strange
because that was my brother's birthday.

441
00:26:41,100 --> 00:26:44,710
My brother's going to be so disappointed
when I marry you.

442
00:26:45,210 --> 00:26:46,310
But what can I do?

443
00:26:46,310 --> 00:26:49,550
I need my life back as Oh Jang Mi.

444
00:26:50,450 --> 00:26:52,120
Everyone is going to be so shocked.

445
00:26:53,520 --> 00:26:54,750
Especially my grandfather.

446
00:26:55,150 --> 00:26:57,420
What if Grandfather is so shocked
that he collapses?

447
00:26:57,490 --> 00:27:01,620
No way. He'll be thrilled to see you.

448
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,970
Is that so?

449
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:33,120
(Violent Crimes Unit 2)

450
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,520
(The First Man)

451
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,430
What? Mom's missing?

452
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:12,630
Someone broke into our house and took Mom!

453
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:15,000
Where is my mom? Where is she?

454
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,830
If you want Jung Suk Hee to live,

455
00:28:17,170 --> 00:28:19,300
bring Oh Bok Gil's cell phone
and memory card.

456
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:21,740
But you have to come alone.

457
00:28:21,740 --> 00:28:23,170
Don't you dare touch my mom!

458
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:26,110
Take care of all the loose ends!

459
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,280
How dare you try to lay a hand on my girl?

460
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:29,780
Baek Ho.

461
00:28:33,650 --> 00:28:35,650
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
